###Block: Combat Tricks
Aldori Dueling Mastery				KEY:Combat Trick ~ Aldori Dueling Mastery	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.24	DESC:You can spend up to 6 stamina points at the start of your turn to increase the shield bonus that you gain from the Aldori Dueling Mastery feat by 1 per 2 stamina points spent until the start of your next turn.
Demon Hunter					KEY:Combat Trick ~ Demon Hunter		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.24	DESC:When you successfully identify a demon using Knowledge (planes), you can spend up to 9 stamina points to increase the morale bonus on attack rolls and caster level checks from Demon Hunter by 1 per 3 stamina points spent.
Desperate Battler					KEY:Combat Trick ~ Desperate Battler	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.24	DESC:You can spend 2 stamina points to gain the benefits of Desperate Battler even while an ally is within 10 feet of you (but not when receiving the benefits of the aid another action).
Flagbearer						KEY:Combat Trick ~ Flagbearer			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.25	DESC:Whenever you can see your f lag but aren't holding it, you can spend 1 stamina point to gain the benefits of Flagbearer for 1 minute as if you were holding it.
Focused Discipline				KEY:Combat Trick ~ Focused Discipline	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.25	DESC:You can spend 2 stamina points in order to gain the benefit of Focused Discipline for 1 round as if you had been targeted by a fear effect that failed to affect you.
Hamatulatsu						KEY:Combat Trick ~ Hamatulatsu		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.25	DESC:By spending 5 stamina points, you can treat a hit with an unarmed strike as a critical hit for the purpose of determining the benefits that you gain from Hamatulatsu.
Shrewd Tactician					KEY:Combat Trick ~ Shrewd Tactician		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.25	DESC:When an opponent attempts a feint against you, you can spend up to 5 stamina points to increase the DC of the skill check made to feint by 1 per point of stamina spent.
Taldan Duelist					KEY:Combat Trick ~ Taldan Duelist		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Combat Trick.SpecialQuality.Combat			SOURCEPAGE:p.25	DESC:When you make an attack with a falcata using two hands while wearing a buckler, you can spend 3 stamina points to ignore the -1 penalty on attack rolls for using your shield arm to wield a weapon while wearing a buckler and to retain the buckler's shield bonus for 1 round.
